    <p>Wrap the <code>&lt;table&gt;</code> in a <code>&lt;div class="table-wrapper"&gt;</code> to allow horizontal scrolling on narrow viewports without breaking the page layout.</p>
    
    <div class="padding-m margin-y-m background-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200">
<div class="table-wrapper">
  <table style="min-width: 40rem">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th scope="col">Server</th>
